158
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:21,417
We're helping these
people because we can,

159
00:07:21,467 --> 00:07:24,050
and if this situation were reversed,

160
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,560
how lucky would we be to meet

161
00:07:25,610 --> 00:07:27,492
