235
00:10:30,165 --> 00:10:32,880
(crickets chirping)

236
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:35,540
- You're out there seein' the world.

237
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:36,883
Experiencin' things.

238
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:40,863
